{"data":[{"date":"15:04 02/08","title":"Logo bia S\u00e0i G\u00f2n s\u1ebd xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u1edf gi\u1ea3i ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/2/logo-bia-sai-gon-se-xuat-hien-o-giai-ngoai-hang-anh-201819.jpg","new_desc":"${8_news_content2}","new_url":"","id":"4984","checkdouble":"192550"},{"date":"15:07 02/08","title":"Si\u00eau sao Ronaldo gi\u00fap Juventus ph\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c tr\u00ean YouTube","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/2/sieu-sao-ronaldo-giup-juventus-pha-ky-luc-tren-youtube.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Gia nh\u1eadp ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea7y m\u1ed9t th\u00e1ng, CR7 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Serie A tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh CLB b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean trang chia s\u1ebb video YouTube.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">Trong th\u00e1ng B\u1ea3y, Juventus \u0111\u1ea1t kho\u1ea3ng 36,3 tri\u1ec7u l\u01b0\u1ee3t xem tr\u00ean YouTube. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 con s\u1ed1 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 khi \u0111\u1eb7t c\u1ea1nh 18,3 tri\u1ec7u m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trong... s\u00e1u th\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m tr\u00ean k\u00eanh n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCon s\u1ed1 36,3 tri\u1ec7u c\u0169ng gi\u00fap Juventus v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Barca, \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh CLB b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t trong c\u00f9ng k\u1ef3. Barca \u0111ang x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 hai v\u1edbi 31,9 tri\u1ec7u l\u01b0\u1ee3t xem, c\u00f2n Real Madrid x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 ba v\u1edbi 24,4 tri\u1ec7u.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"K\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a Juventus tr\u00ean Youtube \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft l\u1eadp nh\u1edd Ronaldo h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"K\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a Juventus tr\u00ean Youtube \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft l\u1eadp nh\u1edd Ronaldo h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/2/rona2-3315-1533182047.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">K\u00eanh c\u1ee7a Juventus hi\u1ec7n c\u00f3 h\u01a1n 1,2 tri\u1ec7u t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n theo d\u00f5i.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng 4/2018, Juventus ch\u1ec9 x\u1ebfp \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed 11 trong danh s\u00e1ch (v\u1edbi 2,9 tri\u1ec7u l\u01b0\u1ee3t xem). Trong th\u00e1ng 5 v\u00e0 6, h\u1ecd nh\u00edch l\u00ean th\u1ee9 9, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn c\u00fa \u0111\u1ed9t ph\u00e1 ngo\u1ea1n m\u1ee5c trong th\u00e1ng 7.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Italy c\u00f3 s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3t xem nhi\u1ec1u th\u1ee9 hai trong th\u00e1ng 7 l\u00e0 Inter Milan ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1t 2,8 tri\u1ec7u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nRonaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus h\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng 7, sau cu\u1ed9c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1eeb Real. Si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha m\u1edbi ra m\u1eaft v\u00e0 t\u1eadp v\u00e0i bu\u1ed5i nh\u01b0ng t\u1ea1o s\u1ee9c h\u00fat ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng l\u1edbn cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi. </div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4983","checkdouble":"192551"},{"date":"17:36 02/08","title":"3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u1ebfu Gonzalo Higuain t\u1edbi AC Milan","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/2/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-neu-gonzalo-higuain-toi-ac-milan.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Gonzalo Higuain t\u1edbi AC Milan \u0111ang l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao, d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 danh s\u00e1ch 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u1ebfu ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn San Siro.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Leonardo</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u, AC Milan \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh sa th\u1ea3i Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao Massimiliano Mirabelli, sau \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u h\u1ecd b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 Leonardo.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Gonzalo Higuain t\u1edbi AC Milan Ai vui ai bu\u1ed3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Gonzalo Higuain t\u1edbi AC Milan Ai vui ai bu\u1ed3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/2/Gonzalo-Higuain-toi-AC-Milan-Ai-vui-ai-buon-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Leonardo l\u1eadp chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch khi \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Higuain</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u00f3i v\u1ec1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Leonardo l\u00e0m Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao, ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Paolo Scaroni c\u1ee7a AC Milan kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh: &ldquo;Leonardo s\u1ebd ch\u1ecbu tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ec1&nbsp;l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c th\u1ec3 thao c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng, b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng 2018&rdquo;.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vai tr\u00f2 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi nh\u1eb1m t\u0103ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea1nh tranh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, Leonardo \u0111\u00e3 t\u00edch c\u1ef1c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. AC Milan \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua Higuain t\u1eeb Juventus.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1987 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng trung phong t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2n s\u00fat 31 tu\u1ed5i gi\u00fap kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea1nh tranh c\u1ee7a AC Milan \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong 42 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, AC Milan ch\u1ec9 ghi c\u00f3 56 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. H\u1ecd \u0111ang thi\u1ebfu \u0111i m\u1ed9t trung phong \u1edf \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p cao v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung t\u1eeb Higuain l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft.&nbsp;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-italia/higuain-dong-y-toi-milan-176-192414.html\" target=\"_blank\">Gonzalo Higuain t\u1edbi AC Milan</span>, HLV Gatusso c\u00f3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t t\u00e2n binh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u00f2n Leonardo ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn ghi \u0111i\u1ec3m trong m\u1eaft ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Scaroni.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Alvaro Morata</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Alvaro Morata kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh: &ldquo;M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i Chelsea v\u1edbi t\u00f4i kh\u00e1 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i \u0111ang n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Chelsea&rdquo;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Morata co them co hoi khang dinh minh o Chelsea\" title=\"Morata c\u00f3 th\u00eam c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u00ecnh \u1edf Chelsea\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/2/morata.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Morata c\u00f3 th\u00eam c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u00ecnh \u1edf Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nMorata mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u1edf Chelsea, song HLV Sarri d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u00edch phong c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i, \u00f4ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea9y anh ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u0169 Gonzalo Higuain.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eed ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ebfn Italia \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n mua Higuain, song l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Juventus nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. L\u00fac n\u00e0y, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 31 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 \u1edf r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n AC Milan, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 The Blues mua th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5p.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Higuain, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng HLV Sarri s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Morata \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. Ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha s\u1ebd l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 th\u00eam c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u00ecnh sau m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng \u1edf Stamford Bridge.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Leonardo Bonucci</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Leonardo Bonucci c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn AC Milan \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2017 v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 42 tri\u1ec7u euro, v\u1edbi kinh nghi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh anh ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Milan v\u1edbi h\u01a1n 50 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bonucci tro lai Juventus chi sau mot mua giai ra di\" title=\"Bonucci tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Juventus ch\u1ec9 sau m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i ra \u0111i\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/2/bonucci.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Bonucci tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Juventus ch\u1ec9 sau m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i ra \u0111i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, s\u1ef1 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a Bonucci kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap AC Milan gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 d\u1ef1 Champions League m\u00f9a t\u1edbi, h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 6 \u1edf Serie A m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i. N\u1ebfu ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n San Siro, s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 31 tu\u1ed5i h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nJuventus x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn Bonucci s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Gonzalo Higuain. Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady l\u00e0 sau 1 n\u0103m ra \u0111i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1987 l\u1ea1i tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Juventus.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKhi m\u00e0 Rugani s\u1eafp t\u1edbi Chelsea c\u00f2n Giorgio Chiellini v\u00e0 Andrea Barzagli \u0111\u00e3 l\u1edbn tu\u1ed5i, Bonucci ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: HLV Maurizio Sarri</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Maurizio Sarri r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u0169 Gonzalo Higuain t\u1eeb Juventus \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian g\u1eafn b\u00f3 c\u00f9ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 31 tu\u1ed5i \u1edf Napoli, \u00f4ng bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 khai th\u00e1c t\u1ed1i \u0111a kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Sarri khong the tai hop voi Higuain o Chelsea\" title=\"HLV Sarri kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi Higuain \u1edf Chelsea\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/2/juve-mua-bonucci-milan-muon-higuain.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Sarri kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi Higuain \u1edf Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 58 tu\u1ed5i s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n c\u1ea3 Morata v\u00e0 Olivier Giroud \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n c\u1ee7a&nbsp;Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn HLV Sarri h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng. The Blues ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn Higuain tr\u01b0\u1edbc AC Milan, nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf v\u00e0o tay c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng&nbsp;th\u00e0nh Milan.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Higuain, HLV Sarri s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ph\u1ea3i s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nh\u1eefng nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 \u0111ang c\u00f3 trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh l\u00e0 Morata v\u00e0 Giroud. S\u1ebd l\u00e0 th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda v\u1edbi c\u1ef1u HLV Napoli n\u1ebfu \u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 Higuain v\u00e0 c\u00f2n m\u1ea5t th\u00eam Eden Hazard ho\u1eb7c Willian trong th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: Cristiano Ronaldo</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gonzalo Higuain v\u00e0 Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 4 n\u0103m ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh nhau \u1edf Real Madrid, trong kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u00f3 b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i n\u00e0y s\u00e1t c\u00e1nh b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh nhau 80 l\u1ea7n, ghi t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 250 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ronaldo khong the choi ben canh Higuain mot lan nua\" title=\"Ronaldo kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh Higuain m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/2/ronaldo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ronaldo kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh Higuain m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHiguain v\u00e0 Ronaldo k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi nhau trong qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian \u1edf Bernabeu, NHM Juventus hy v\u1ecdng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin. B\u1ea3n th\u00e2n CR7 c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1987.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1edbi ch\u00e2n \u01b0\u1edbt ch\u00e2n r\u00e1o \u0111\u1ebfn Juventus, Ronaldo c\u1ea7n s\u1ef1 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 c\u1ee7a Higuain \u0111\u1ec3 h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp nhanh nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia. Tuy nhi\u00ean, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m r\u1eddi Juventus, anh kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n thi \u0111\u1ea5u d\u01b0\u1edbi c\u00e1i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Ronaldo.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1eadp b\u1ebfn AC Milan, Higuain s\u1ebd c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ea1nh tranh danh hi\u1ec7u Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi Serie A v\u1edbi si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: Nicola Kalinic</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nicola Kalinic l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda \u1edf World Cup 2018. Ng\u00f4i sao 30 tu\u1ed5i t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Croatia \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng v\u00ec l\u00fd do ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u01b0ng, h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn anh b\u1ecb HLV Zlatko Dalic t\u1ed1ng c\u1ed5 v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nicola Kalinic nhieu kha nang se ngoi du bi cho Higuain\" title=\"Nicola Kalinic nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb cho Higuain\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/2/kalinic.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nicola Kalinic nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb cho Higuain</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nCroatia sau \u0111\u00f3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 song Nicola Kalinic th\u00ec m\u1ea5t \u0111i\u1ec3m nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng trong m\u1eaft NHM. M\u00f9a H\u00e8 kh\u1ee7ng khi\u1ebfp c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 30 tu\u1ed5i n\u1ebfu Higuain c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Juventus.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Nicola Kalinic ch\u1ec9 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 6 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng sau 31 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n \u1edf Serie A, ch\u00ednh th\u00e0nh t\u00edch khi\u00eam t\u1ed1n n\u00e0y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn AC Milan kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 v\u00e9 d\u1ef1 Champions League m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea9y Nicola Kalinic l\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n* Squawka</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4982","checkdouble":"192568"},{"date":"12:17 02/08","title":"HLV Park Hang Seo tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd tr\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/19/hlv-park-hang-seo-tuyen-bo-manh-me-truoc-giai-giao-huu-quoc-te-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u trong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf c\u00fap Vinaphone 2018, HLV Park Hang Seo cho bi\u1ebft Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd thi \u0111\u1ea5u nghi\u00eam t\u00fac v\u1edbi quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m cao nh\u1ea5t.</h2><h2>HLV Park Hang Seo kh\u00f4ng xem nh\u1eb9 gi\u1ea3i t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ASIAD 2018, L\u0110B\u0110 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f9ng nh\u00e0 t\u00e0i tr\u1ee3 Vinaphone \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf gi\u1eefa \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Uzbekistan, Palestine v\u00e0 Oman.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u quy t\u1ee5 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1eadp d\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u00e0 c\u00f3 b\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ea1y \u0111\u00e0 ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o cho gi\u1ea3i ch\u00e2u \u00c1 s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<br />\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Park Hang Seo tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd tr\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Park Hang Seo tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd tr\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/hang-thu-olympic-viet-nam-su-tu-tin-cua-thay-park.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Park Hang Seo kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh&nbsp;Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u00eat s\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i c\u00fap t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng s\u1eafp t\u1edbi</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u trong cu\u1ed9c h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o tr\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u1ea3i s\u00e1ng nay 2/8, v\u1ecb thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam HLV Park Hang Seo kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd cho c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn v\u00ec NHM.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i trong gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y l\u00e0 ki\u1ec3m tra n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c 20 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 n\u00e2ng cao chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng t\u1edbi gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i ch\u01a1i. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 coi nh\u1eb9 gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu n\u00e0y. L\u00e0 m\u1ed9t hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1edf m\u1ecdi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00ecnh tham d\u1ef1&rdquo;, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c chia s\u1ebb.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 th\u1ea7y Park tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 kh\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd nh\u01b0 v\u1eady tuy nhi\u00ean s\u1ebd kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi c\u00e1c tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi 100% th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bao-han-khong-danh-gia-cao-olympic-viet-nam-tai-asiad-2018-168-192541.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/2/bao-han-khong-danh-gia-cao-olympic-viet-nam-tai-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bao-han-khong-danh-gia-cao-olympic-viet-nam-tai-asiad-2018-168-192541.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018</span><br />\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, t\u1edd b\u00e1o \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1eed H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nNgay c\u1ea3 th\u1ea7y Park tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn: &quot;N\u1ebfu c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u01a1n 100% kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu r\u1ed3i g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng khi s\u1eafp \u0111\u1ebfn gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c th\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 m\u1edbi l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ea7n quan t\u00e2m. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t . T\u00f4i mong m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi hi\u1ec3u \u0111\u00e2u m\u1edbi l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a&nbsp;U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng, d\u00f9 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0o th\u00ec v\u1eabn h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau cao nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng nh\u01b0ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 h\u1ecd c\u00f3 gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n. \u0110i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 t\u00f4i v\u00e0 c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 l\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m sao \u0111\u1eb7t \u0111i\u1ec3m r\u01a1i, phong \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0o gi\u1ea3i ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c m\u1edbi l\u00e0 quan tr\u1ecdng&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ra qu\u00e2n v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i mai 3/8 g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 U23 Palestine. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ec1u s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 chi\u1ec1u cao \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Do \u0111\u00f3, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1eadp trung, c\u1ea9n th\u1eadn \u0111\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t.<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;&#10;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4981","checkdouble":"192542"},{"date":"14:26 02/08","title":"HLV Uzbekistan \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/hlv-uzbekistan-an-tuong-voi-hai-cau-thu-cua-olympic-viet-nam.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb trong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o tr\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng c\u00fap Vinaphone 2018, HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T U23 Uzbekistan \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</h2><h2>HLV Uzbekistan \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Vi\u1ec7t Nam</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><em><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Uzbekistan \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Uzbekistan \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/1/27/HLV-Uzbekistan-an-tuong-voi-hai-cau-thu-cua-Olympic-Viet-Nam-hinh-anh.jpg\" /></em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Uzbekistan \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Quang H\u1ea3i</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u00e1ng 2/8 t\u1ea1i tr\u1ee5 s\u1edf L\u0110B\u0110 Vi\u1ec7t Nam, VFF \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o tr\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng c\u00fap Vinaphone 2018. C\u00f3 m\u1eb7t trong s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n n\u00e0y, HLV \u0110T U23 Uzbekistan HLV Ravshan Khaydarov \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ecb n\u00e0y th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n k\u1ec3 t\u00ean hai ng\u00f4i sao m\u00e0 \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t b\u00ean ph\u00eda \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf bao g\u1ed3m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 mang \u00e1o s\u1ed1 7 (H\u1ed3ng Duy) v\u00e0 s\u1ed1 19 (Quang H\u1ea3i).\u00a0</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\"Sau tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i thu th\u1eadp nhi\u1ec1u th\u00f4ng tin h\u01a1n v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eed chuy\u00ean gia theo d\u00f5i c\u00e1c b\u0103ng h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam. Hy v\u1ecdng r\u1eb1ng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1eafp t\u1edbi hai \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u00eam s\u1ef1 c\u1ecd x\u00e1t v\u1edbi nhau,\" HLV Uzbekistan, Ravshan Khaydarov n\u00f3i.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n n\u00e0y c\u0169ng b\u1eadt m\u00ed, \u00f4ng r\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i v\u00e0 cho r\u1eb1ng U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam th\u00edch nghi v\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n th\u1eddi ti\u1ebft r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T U23 Uzbekistan s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i U23+3 c\u1ee7a Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 7/8 t\u1edbi. Th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo c\u0169ng x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 nguy hi\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5t m\u00e0 h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-tuyen-bo-manh-me-truoc-giai-giao-huu-quoc-te-2018-168-192542.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/19/hlv-park-hang-seo-tuyen-bo-manh-me-truoc-giai-giao-huu-quoc-te-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-tuyen-bo-manh-me-truoc-giai-giao-huu-quoc-te-2018-168-192542.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd tr\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf 2018</span><br />\r\nPh\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u trong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf c\u00fap Vinaphone 2018, HLV Park Hang Seo cho bi\u1ebft Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd thi \u0111\u1ea5u nghi\u00eam t\u00fac v\u1edbi...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bao-han-khong-danh-gia-cao-olympic-viet-nam-tai-asiad-2018-168-192541.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/2/bao-han-khong-danh-gia-cao-olympic-viet-nam-tai-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bao-han-khong-danh-gia-cao-olympic-viet-nam-tai-asiad-2018-168-192541.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018</span><br />\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, t\u1edd b\u00e1o \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1eed H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c KBS News \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4980","checkdouble":"192545"},{"date":"14:37 02/08","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U16 Indonesia 18h30 ng\u00e0y 2/8 (U16 AFF Cup 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/2/u16-viet-nam-vs-u16-indonesia-aff-cup-2018-hom-nay.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U16 Indonesia: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng video clip k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 k\u00e8m link xem tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U16 Indonesia gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch U16 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 AFF Cup 2018 l\u00fac 18h30 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 2/8</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">(\u1ea5n Ctrl + F5 \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t)<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u to\u00e0n th\u1eafng, U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i duy nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng A ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi b\u00e0n n\u00e0o. Tuy nhi\u00ean, s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 HLV V\u0169 H\u1ed3ng Vi\u1ec7t m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 d\u1eebng \u1edf con s\u1ed1 5 n\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ea1m th\u1eddi x\u1ebfp \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 2 sau U16 Indonesia. <br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U16 Indonesia AFF Cup 2018 h\u00f4m nay 28 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U16 Indonesia AFF Cup 2018 h\u00f4m nay 28 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/2/Truc-tiep-U16-Viet-Nam-vs-U16-Indonesia-AFF-Cup-2018-hom-nay-28-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">X\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng A sau 2 l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nK\u1ec3 t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u gi\u1ea3i, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00e1ng n\u1ec3: Th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm U16 Philippines v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 8-0 v\u00e0 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua U16 Myanmar v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-1. L\u1ee3i th\u1ebf s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn U16 Indonesia tr\u1edf n\u00ean r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng g\u1eddm v\u1edbi U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam. T\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng A, U16 Indonesia \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t, n\u00ean n\u1ebfu gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y th\u00ec c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn 90% kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n nay, U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t, l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i g\u1eafn k\u1ebft v\u00e0 s\u1edf h\u1eefu nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9t bi\u1ebfn, trong \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 Nguy\u00ean Ho\u00e0ng. Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o thu\u1ed9c l\u00f2 \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o PVF c\u00f3 chi\u1ec1u cao l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn 1m80 n\u00ean r\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i h\u1ea1i trong kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfn.<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U16 Indonesia 18h30 ng\u00e0y 28 (U16 AFF Cup 2018) h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U16 Indonesia 18h30 ng\u00e0y 28 (U16 AFF Cup 2018) h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/28/TRUC-TIEP-U16-Viet-Nam-vs-U16-Indonesia-18h30-ngay-28-(U16-AFF-Cup-2018)-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Danh s\u00e1ch tuy\u1ec3n U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam tham d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i U16 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4979","checkdouble":"192547"},{"date":"15:08 02/08","title":"HLV Palestine n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/2/hlv-palestine-noi-gi-ve-olympic-viet-nam.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>V\u1ecb HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng U23 Palestine \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1ec1 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam trong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o tr\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng c\u00fap Vinaphone 2018 s\u00e1ng 2/8.</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00e0 m\u1ed9t kh\u00e1ch m\u1eddi c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu U23 Qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf c\u00fap Vinaphone 2018, trong chi\u1ec1u qua 1/8, \u0110T U23 Palestine \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam. \u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 l\u00e0 'qu\u00e2n xanh' l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng cho \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ASIAD 2018.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV U23 Palestine n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV U23 Palestine n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/2/img_9591-1354.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV U23 Palestine c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen cho \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Vi\u1ec7t Nam</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u00e1ng 2/8, HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T U23 Palestine \u00f4ng Sandouqa c\u0169ng tham d\u1ef1 bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o tr\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u1ea3i do VFF t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c.\u00a0Chia s\u1ebb trong s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n n\u00e0y, v\u1ecb thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Palestine cho hay: \"Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 v\u00ec b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018, v\u00ec th\u1ebf ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u00edt ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1eadp h\u1ee3p v\u00e0 sang Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i U23 T\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng.</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng, b\u1edfi v\u00ec 3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n M\u1ef9 \u0110\u00ecnh s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u00e0n t\u1eadp d\u01b0\u1ee3t ch\u00ednh, trong khi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian, m\u00e0 ASIAD th\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 g\u1ea7n k\u1ec1. Sau gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u01b0a t\u00ecm ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c qu\u00e2n xanh \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ecd s\u00e1t\".</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo v\u1ecb thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a U23 Palestine cho bi\u1ebft, \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Palestine \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u00ean 23 tu\u1ed5i nh\u01b0 trong \u0111i\u1ec1u l\u1ec7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy \u0111\u1ecbnh, b\u1edfi 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1 ASIAD Cup m\u00e0 s\u1ebd chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho Asian Cup n\u0103m sau.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 v\u1ec1 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam, HLV Sandouqa \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e0nh r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u l\u1eddi t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p: \"U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 U23 Palestine \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p nhau \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu t\u1ea1i Trung Qu\u1ed1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u1ea3i U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018 v\u1eeba qua. T\u00f4i quan s\u00e1t th\u1ea5y c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Vi\u1ec7t Nam r\u1ea5t nhanh, kh\u00e9o, h\u1ecd di chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed3ng b\u1ed9 c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t, v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n c\u1ea3 m\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi ngo\u00e0i nh\u01b0 t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t gia \u0111\u00ecnh\".</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u, \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n c\u00f9ng U23 Palestine v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 03/08 t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edf v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng HLV hai \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 thay v\u00ec quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-uzbekistan-an-tuong-voi-hai-cau-thu-cua-olympic-viet-nam-168-192545.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/hlv-uzbekistan-an-tuong-voi-hai-cau-thu-cua-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-uzbekistan-an-tuong-voi-hai-cau-thu-cua-olympic-viet-nam-168-192545.html\">HLV Uzbekistan \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br />\r\nChia s\u1ebb trong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o tr\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng c\u00fap Vinaphone 2018, HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T U23 Uzbekistan \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-tuyen-bo-manh-me-truoc-giai-giao-huu-quoc-te-2018-168-192542.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/19/hlv-park-hang-seo-tuyen-bo-manh-me-truoc-giai-giao-huu-quoc-te-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-tuyen-bo-manh-me-truoc-giai-giao-huu-quoc-te-2018-168-192542.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd tr\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf 2018</span><br />\r\nPh\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u trong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf c\u00fap Vinaphone 2018, HLV Park Hang Seo cho bi\u1ebft Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd thi \u0111\u1ea5u nghi\u00eam t\u00fac v\u1edbi...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4978","checkdouble":"192552"},{"date":"17:44 02/08","title":"L\u0110B\u0110 Iraq ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn vi\u1ec7c r\u00fat \u0110T Olympic Iraq kh\u1ecfi ASIAD 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/1/18/ldbd-iraq-phu-nhan-viec-rut-dt-olympic-iraq-khoi-asiad-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong m\u1ed9t di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, t\u1edd Reuters cho r\u1eb1ng L\u0110B\u0110 Iraq ch\u01b0a h\u1ec1 tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 r\u00fat \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Olympic Iraq kh\u1ecfi ASIAD 2018.</h2><h2>L\u0110B\u0110 Iraq ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn vi\u1ec7c r\u00fat \u0110T Olympic Iraq kh\u1ecfi ASIAD\u00a0</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a, sau khi \u0111\u1ed9i U16 Iraq b\u1ecb ph\u00e1t hi\u1ec7n gian l\u1eadn tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u00f4ng tin L\u0110B\u0110 n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng tham d\u1ef1 m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"L\u0110B\u0110 Iraq ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn vi\u1ec7c r\u00fat \u0110T Olympic Iraq kh\u1ecfi ASIAD 2018  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"L\u0110B\u0110 Iraq ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn vi\u1ec7c r\u00fat \u0110T Olympic Iraq kh\u1ecfi ASIAD 2018  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/1/18/ldbd-iraq-phu-nhan-viec-rut-dt-olympic-iraq-khoi-asiad-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 chuy\u1ec7n\u00a0\u0110T Olympic Iraq r\u00fat kh\u1ecfi ASIAD 2018 nh\u01b0 tin \u0111\u1ed3n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u00e3ng Reuters th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n \u0111\u1eb7t c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng BTC ASIAD 18 s\u1ebd m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa ph\u1ea3i b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam b\u1edfi c\u01a1 c\u1ea5u c\u00e1c b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 c\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed1i do b\u1ea3ng C ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00fang 3 \u0111\u1ed9i l\u00e0 Trung Qu\u1ed1c, \u0110\u00f4ng Timor v\u00e0 Syria, trong khi b\u1ea3ng A v\u00e0 E c\u00f3 t\u1edbi 5 \u0111\u1ed9i.</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean ngay sau \u0111\u00f3, Reuters, h\u00e3ng th\u00f4ng t\u1ea5n uy t\u00edn h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi d\u1eabn ngu\u1ed3n tin t\u1eeb L\u0110B\u0110 Iraq cho bi\u1ebft n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn chuy\u1ec7n s\u1ebd r\u00fat \u0111\u1ed9i Olympic Iraq kh\u1ecfi \u00c1 v\u1eadn h\u1ed9i 2018.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd b\u00e1o n\u00e0y cho bi\u1ebft: \"Iraq v\u1eabn s\u1ebd c\u1eed \u0111\u1ed9i U23 t\u1edbi Indonesia tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018 b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eefng suy \u0111o\u00e1n v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 r\u00fat lui. M\u1ed9t ngu\u1ed3n tin t\u1eeb IFA ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9i U23 s\u1ebd b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u. Ngu\u1ed3n tin n\u00e0y c\u0169ng cho bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ed9i U23 Iraq \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ASIAD, sau khi k\u1ebft th\u00fac \u0111\u1ee3t t\u1eadp hu\u1ea5n t\u1ea1i th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 Erbil \u1edf ph\u00eda b\u1eafc Iraq\".\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018, \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Iraq t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng s\u1ebd l\u00e0 Trung Qu\u1ed1c, \u0110\u00f4ng Timor v\u00e0 Syria. Ngo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb \u0110\u00f4ng Timor th\u00ec hai \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng g\u1eddm trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng trong v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi Iraq.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-palestine-noi-gi-ve-olympic-viet-nam-168-192552.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/2/hlv-palestine-noi-gi-ve-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-palestine-noi-gi-ve-olympic-viet-nam-168-192552.html\">HLV Palestine n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam?</span><br>\r\nV\u1ecb HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng U23 Palestine \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1ec1 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam trong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o tr\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng c\u00fap Vinaphone 2018 s\u00e1ng 2/8.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-uzbekistan-an-tuong-voi-hai-cau-thu-cua-olympic-viet-nam-168-192545.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/hlv-uzbekistan-an-tuong-voi-hai-cau-thu-cua-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-uzbekistan-an-tuong-voi-hai-cau-thu-cua-olympic-viet-nam-168-192545.html\">HLV Uzbekistan \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb trong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o tr\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng c\u00fap Vinaphone 2018, HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T U23 Uzbekistan \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4977","checkdouble":"192566"},{"date":"15:06 02/08","title":"\"Barca l\u00e0 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o v\u1edbi Mignolet\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/12/20/barca-la-ben-do-hoan-hao-cua-mignolet.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Steve Nicol ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Simon Mignolet, ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 c\u1ee7a Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng khuy\u00ean th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 ch\u1ecdn Barca thay v\u00ec \u1edf l\u1ea1i Anfield.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Barca quan t\u00e2m Simon Mignolet</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBarca \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Jasper Cillessen. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 Lan \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1eeb ph\u00eda Chelsea v\u00e0 Napoli, anh mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Steve Nicol ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Simon Mignolet h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Steve Nicol ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Simon Mignolet h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/12/20/barca-la-ben-do-hoan-hao-cua-mignolet.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u00a0Mignolet \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Barca quan t\u00e2m</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1eeb khi chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi s\u00e2n Camp Nou, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb. Anh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u1edbi Marc-Andre ter Stegen.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/barca-chi-11-trieu-bang-mua-cai-ten-khong-the-ngo-toi-cua-liverpool-180-192432.html\" target=\"_blank\">Barca mu\u1ed1n mua Simon Mignolet</span> c\u1ee7a Liverpool trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Jasper Cillessen ra \u0111i. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 11 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1988. Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Barca c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 cao.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Alisson, Mignolet l\u00fac n\u00e0y tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn th\u1ee9 3 trong khung g\u1ed7 c\u1ee7a Liverpool. \u0110\u00edch th\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1988 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u00e2n ch\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111ang t\u00ecm b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Barca, Mignolet nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb cho Marc-Andre ter Stegen, song anh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Mignolet n\u00ean ch\u1ecdn Barca</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Steve Nicol ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Simon Mignolet, ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 c\u1ee7a Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng khuy\u00ean th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 ch\u1ecdn Barca thay v\u00ec \u1edf l\u1ea1i Anfield.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thu thanh Mignolet co kha nang can pha phat den rat tot.\" title=\"Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Mignolet c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/10/16/barca-chi-11-trieu-bang-mua-cai-ten-khong-the-ngo-toi-cua-liverpool.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Steve Nicol khuy\u00ean Mignolet t\u1edbi Barca</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Mignolet ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. \u1ede tu\u1ed5i 30, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 l\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng c\u1ea1nh tranh b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Barca v\u00e0 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n s\u1ed1 2 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cN\u1ebfu Mignolet c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Barca, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o cho c\u1ea3 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 Barca n\u1eefa. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i duy nh\u1ea5t cho Mignolet v\u00e0 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y n\u00ean suy ngh\u0129 r\u1ea5t k\u1ef9, c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Barca n\u1ebfu r\u1eddi Liverpool\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a Mignolet, trong \u0111\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn Napoli v\u00e0 Besiktas. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 v\u1eabn \u0111ang trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4976","checkdouble":"192544"},{"date":"17:21 02/08","title":"M\u00f9a h\u00e8 \u1ea3m \u0111\u1ea1m c\u1ee7a Real Madrid: Sau \u0111\u1ec9nh cao l\u00e0 v\u1ef1c s\u00e2u?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/31/mua-he-am-dam-cua-real-madrid-sau-dinh-cao-la-vuc-sau.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>K\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea7y m\u1ed9t th\u00e1ng nh\u01b0ng nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u v\u1eabn h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c b\u00ecnh ch\u00e2n nh\u01b0 v\u1ea1i, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t trong c\u00f4ng cu\u1ed9c k\u00edch n\u1ed5 bom t\u1ea5n thay th\u1ebf si\u00eau sao Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 ra \u0111i sau 9 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/diem-nhan-sau-chien-thang-rua-mat-cua-mu-truoc-real-184-192465.html\" target=\"_blank\">Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Manchester United</span> tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c m\u1edf m\u00e0n m\u1ed9t k\u1ef7 nguy\u00ean m\u1edbi \u1edf Real Madrid. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean ng\u1ed3i tr\u00ean gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a t\u00e2n HLV Julen Lopetegui v\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n s\u1ef1 hi\u1ec7n di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo, m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i nh\u1ea5t l\u1ecbch s\u1eed s\u00e2n Bernabeu.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u00e2y v\u1eabn ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu kh\u00f4ng mang nhi\u1ec1u \u00fd ngh\u0129a, v\u1eady n\u00ean c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng th\u1ec3 r\u00fat ra k\u1ebft lu\u1eadn g\u00ec th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 x\u00e1c \u0111\u00e1ng cho c\u1ea3 k\u1ebb th\u1eafng l\u1eabn ng\u01b0\u1eddi thua. Hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u thi\u1ebfu v\u1eafng c\u1ea3 t\u00e1 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t, c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 nh\u00f3m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ti\u1ebfn s\u00e2u \u1edf World Cup 2018 c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0110TQG, thay th\u1ebf b\u1eb1ng h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb c\u00f9ng l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu m\u00e0i \u0111\u0169ng qu\u1ea7n tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid h\u00e8 2018 \u1ea3m \u0111\u1ea1m Sau \u0111\u1ec9nh cao l\u00e0 v\u1ef1c s\u00e2u h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid h\u00e8 2018 \u1ea3m \u0111\u1ea1m Sau \u0111\u1ec9nh cao l\u00e0 v\u1ef1c s\u00e2u h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/4-ly-do-tin-rang-los-blancos-se-sup-do-o-mua-giai-toi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid h\u00e8 2018 v\u1eabn t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed9ng sau s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 th\u00edch th\u00fa khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn t\u00e2n binh th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil Vinicius Junior s\u00e1t c\u00e1nh b\u00ean nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao Gareth Bale v\u00e0 Karim Benzema tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng Real Madrid, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e2y r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n t\u1ed1i \u01b0u c\u1ee7a Lopetegui cho chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch ra m\u1eaft s\u1eafp t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, \u00edt nh\u1ea5t cho \u0111\u1ebfn khi k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00f3ng c\u1eeda v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i th\u00e1ng T\u00e1m.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i, \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n ch\u00ednh mi\u1ec7ng nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n \u0111ang b\u1ecb c\u1ea3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha gh\u00e9t n\u00e0y g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u: <em>\u201cN\u1ebfu \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u00e0nh v\u1edbi t\u00f4i trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, t\u00f4i c\u0169ng s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac r\u1ed3i.\u201d</em> \u2013 Vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh Bernabeu kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00f3n th\u00eam b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 t\u00e2n binh n\u00e0o ch\u1ee9 \u0111\u1eebng n\u00f3i \u0111\u1ebfn qu\u1ea3 bom t\u1ea5n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf CR7, \u0111\u00e1ng lo ng\u1ea1i l\u00e0 \u0111ang l\u1edd m\u1edd hi\u1ec3n hi\u1ec7n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"M\u00f9a h\u00e8 \u1ea3m \u0111\u1ea1m c\u1ee7a Real Madrid Sau \u0111\u1ec9nh cao l\u00e0 v\u1ef1c s\u00e2u h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"M\u00f9a h\u00e8 \u1ea3m \u0111\u1ea1m c\u1ee7a Real Madrid Sau \u0111\u1ec9nh cao l\u00e0 v\u1ef1c s\u00e2u h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/2/Mua-he-am-dam-cua-Real-Madrid-Sau-dinh-cao-la-vuc-sau-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid h\u00e8 2018 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00ecnh th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng Vinicius \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 sung cho h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Lopetegui khi nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 Bale v\u00e0 Benzema qua nh\u1eefng l\u1ea7n ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean tr\u00ean s\u00e2n t\u1eadp. Ho\u1eb7c \u00f4ng \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u1edf Bernabeu trong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, ho\u1eb7c \u00f4ng \u0111ang v\u1ee5ng v\u1ec1 tr\u1ea5n an d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn v\u00e0 ki\u1ec1m h\u00e3m k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng bom t\u1ea5n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u00dd \u0111\u1ed3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 l\u00e0 g\u00ec, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u00e1c Madridista kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng, vui v\u1ebb g\u00ec d\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 ch\u00fat \u00edt n\u1ebfu t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ed1t cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi, quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1eafn v\u00e0 x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng c\u00f3 cho m\u00ecnh c\u00e1i quy\u1ec1n \u0111\u00f3.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ngay t\u1eeb tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ea3 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-italia/juventus-chieu-mo-cristiano-ronaldo-co-nhung-gia-tri-con-lon-hon-tien-176-191505.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ronaldo s\u1ebd ra \u0111i v\u00e0 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Juventus</span>, \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n g\u1ea7n xa \u0111\u00e3 \u00fap m\u1edf cho nh\u1eefng th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 th\u1ebf k\u1ef7 mang t\u00ean Neymar, Kylian Mbappe, Eden Hazard hay Harry Kane, hay \u00edt nh\u1ea5t c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i \u201cch\u1eefa ch\u00e1y\u201d \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng Robert Lewandowski hay Edinson Cavani. T\u1edbi gi\u1edd n\u00e0y, ch\u1eb3ng ai trong s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y c\u00f3 d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u l\u1ea1c quan s\u1ebd gia nh\u1eadp Real Madrid trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/4-ly-do-tin-rang-los-blancos-se-sup-do-o-mua-giai-toi-180-192418.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/31/4-ly-do-tin-rang-los-blancos-se-sup-do-o-mua-giai-toi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/4-ly-do-tin-rang-los-blancos-se-sup-do-o-mua-giai-toi-180-192418.html\">4 l\u00fd do tin r\u1eb1ng Los Blancos s\u1ebd s\u1ee5p \u0111\u1ed5 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi</span><br>\r\nL\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i nh\u1ea5t \u1edf th\u1ebf k\u1ef7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u0111ang trong th\u1eddi k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ec9nh cao v\u1edbi li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u, tuy nhi\u00ean c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u00fd do Real Madrid s\u1ee5p \u0111\u1ed5 \u1edf m\u00f9a...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n g\u00ec thay \u0111\u1ed5i, hi\u1ec3n nhi\u00ean nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u s\u1ebd suy y\u1ebfu so v\u1edbi ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 t\u1ec7 h\u01a1n n\u1eefa, hai \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 x\u1ebfp tr\u00ean h\u1ecd \u1edf La Liga m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i l\u1ea1i c\u00e0ng m\u1ea1nh l\u00ean. Barcelona chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Clement Lenglet, Arthur Melo v\u00e0 Malcom, trong khi Atletico Madrid \u0111\u00f3n th\u00eam nh\u1eefng Rodri, Thomas Lemar v\u00e0 Gelson Martins.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Real Madrid th\u00ec sao? H\u1ecd c\u00f3 Vinicius nh\u01b0ng \u1edf tu\u1ed5i ch\u01b0a n\u1ed5i \u0111\u00f4i m\u01b0\u01a1i, th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil c\u00f3 l\u1ebd c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c dung d\u01b0\u1ee1ng, quy ho\u1ea1ch cho t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai ch\u1ee9 ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t ngay l\u00fac n\u00e0y. Alvaro Odriozola c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh h\u00e0nh lang c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i v\u1edbi Dani Carvajal v\u00e0 Nacho nh\u01b0ng t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean r\u1ed3i, anh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi Ronaldo ngay t\u1eeb v\u1ecb tr\u00ed thi \u0111\u1ea5u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed ngay c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng Bale hay Benzema c\u00f9ng tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u00e0ng ho\u00e0ng c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb1ng kh\u00e1c c\u01a1 m\u00e0. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 c\u00f3 ti\u1ebfng t\u0103m vung ti\u1ec1n kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ngh\u0129, Real Madrid tr\u00ean th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf chi ti\u00eau \u00edt h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n Barca v\u00e0 Atletico trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m qua.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bale Benzema\" title=\"Bale Benzema\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/2/171113-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid h\u00e8 2018 \u1ea3m \u0111\u1ea1m \u0111\u1ebfn n\u1ed7i ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00f2n tin t\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Bale v\u00e0 Benzema</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">C\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng m\u00e0 n\u00f3i, CLB ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 v\u00e0 \u0111ang r\u1ea5t th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111i m\u1edbi kh\u00f3 tin \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Ronaldo c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u1ea3 Zidane, gi\u1edbi ch\u1ee7 Los Blancos ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafc kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u1ec9 trung th\u00e0nh v\u1edbi c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o v\u00e0 s\u0103n \u0111\u00f3n c\u00e1c t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb m\u00e3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ng\u1ef1 tr\u1ecb tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ec9nh cao th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Madridistas v\u1eabn s\u1ebd s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng khoan dung v\u1edbi th\u00eam m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft th\u00fac \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 ba La Liga n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng con c\u01b0ng ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League. Nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p \u00e1ch th\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecb v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ed1i trong ba n\u0103m g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o cho vinh quang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u1ed1i d\u00e0i tr\u00ean tr\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c h\u1ebft. M\u1ea5u ch\u1ed1t trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e2u c\u00f2n m\u1ed9t Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u1ebfn 43 b\u00e0n/38 tr\u1eadn xuy\u00ean su\u1ed1t h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u0103ng quang ba chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap b\u1ea1c li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t t\u00e2n binh t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Bernabeu trong v\u00f2ng m\u1ed9t th\u00e1ng t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Real Madrid \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n kh\u1ecfi m\u01a1 c\u1ea1nh tranh c\u00e1c danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn t\u1eeb trong n\u01b0\u1edbc ra ngo\u00e0i tr\u1eddi \u00c2u, k\u00e9o theo thi\u1ec7n ch\u00ed c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c C\u0110V kh\u00f3 t\u00ednh v\u00e0 tai qu\u00e1i b\u1eadc nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 r\u1ed3i s\u1ebd nhanh ch\u00f3ng ti\u00eau tan. H\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng hay l\u00e0 ch\u1ebft, b\u00e2y gi\u1edd ho\u1eb7c kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd, Florentino Perez!<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<h2><strong>Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid h\u00e8 2018:</strong><strong><br>\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-201819-khoi-nguyen-cho-zidane-va-pavon-thuc-su-180-192419.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/31/real-madrid-201819-khoi-nguyen-cho-zidane-va-pavon-thuc-su.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-201819-khoi-nguyen-cho-zidane-va-pavon-thuc-su-180-192419.html\">Real Madrid 2018-19: Kh\u1edfi nguy\u00ean cho Zidane v\u00e0 Pavon th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1</span><br>\r\nS\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo, r\u1ed3i Zinedine Zidane nh\u01b0 b\u00e1o hi\u1ec7u s\u1ef1 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t k\u1ef7 nguy\u00ean. Real Madrid li\u1ec7u c\u00f3 \u0111\u1eb7t d\u1ea5u ch\u1ea5m h\u1ebft cho c\u00e1i g\u1ecdi l\u00e0 Galaticos?</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/goc-real-madrid-hazard-se-rat-on-nhung-thay-the-ronaldo-khong-180-191983.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/25/goc-real-madrid-hazard-se-rat-on-nhung-thay-the-ronaldo-khong.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/goc-real-madrid-hazard-se-rat-on-nhung-thay-the-ronaldo-khong-180-191983.html\">G\u00f3c Real Madrid: Hazard s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t \u1ed5n, nh\u01b0ng thay th\u1ebf Ronaldo? Kh\u00f4ng!</span><br>\r\nT\u00e2n HLV Julen Lopetegui s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i t\u00ecm m\u1ed9t ngu\u1ed3n cung 50 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng/m\u00f9a khi Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ra \u0111i v\u1ec1 v\u1edbi Juventus, nh\u01b0ng \u00f4ng c\u00f3 l\u1ebd kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4975","checkdouble":"192564"},{"date":"16:08 02/08","title":"Koscielny ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m r\u1eddi Arsenal","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/9/koscielny-tiet-lo-thoi-diem-roi-arsenal.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Laurent Koscielny \u00fap m\u1edf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chia tay Arsenal khi h\u1ebft h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London sau \u0111\u00e2y 2 n\u0103m.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trung v\u1ec7 Koscielny hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i ngo\u00e0i v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. Nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng anh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i cho t\u1edbi cu\u1ed1i n\u0103m 2018.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p v\u1eabn k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n g\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 cho Arsenal \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. Nh\u01b0ng Koscielny cho r\u1eb1ng anh \u0111ang chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho nh\u1eefng n\u0103m th\u00e1ng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Emirates khi m\u00e0 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 2 n\u0103m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Koscielny r\u1eddi Arsenal sau khi h\u1ebft h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Koscielny r\u1eddi Arsenal sau khi h\u1ebft h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/9/koscielny-tiet-lo-thoi-diem-roi-arsenal.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Koscielny r\u1eddi Arsenal sau khi h\u1ebft h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cT\u00f4i c\u00f3 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Arsenal t\u1edbi n\u0103m 2020. Sau \u0111\u00f3 \u01b0? T\u00f4i \u0111ang ngh\u0129 t\u1edbi chuy\u1ec7n ra \u0111i nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a bi\u1ebft \u0111i \u0111\u00e2u\u201d, Koscielny chia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean t\u1edd Nice-Matin.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cD\u00f9 sao b\u00e2y gi\u1edd c\u0169ng ch\u01b0a ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 l\u00fac ngh\u0129 t\u1edbi chuy\u1ec7n \u0111\u00f3. T\u00f4i \u0111ang \u1edf Anh, gia \u0111\u00ecnh t\u00f4i c\u0169ng th\u1ebf. Sau n\u0103m nay th\u00ec s\u1ebd c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb7t ra.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u0110i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t b\u00e2y gi\u1edd l\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ecdc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1ch t\u1eadp trung gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft t\u1eebng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t b\u1edfi v\u00ec c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u th\u1ee9 quan tr\u1ecdng trong cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang ta\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\nKoscielny \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 320 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n cho Arsenal k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi \u0111\u1ebfn thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Emirates n\u0103m 2010. Anh ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 24 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Koscielny kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n trong n\u1eeda \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, Arsenal c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng nh\u1eefng ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n thay th\u1ebf. HLV Emery \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam nh\u1eefng nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 kh\u00e1c cho h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 nh\u01b0 Sokratis hay Lichtsteiner. \u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u1ec9 huy t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng thay th\u1ebf tr\u1ecdng tr\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Arsenal.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Arsenal:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/lacazette-noi-gi-sau-mua-giai-khong-qua-an-tuong-cung-arsenal-172-192537.html\">Lacazette n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u00f9ng Arsenal?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhung-diem-sang-toi-nhin-tu-chien-thang-cua-arsenal-truoc-chelsea-172-192524.html\">Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u00e1ng t\u1ed1i nh\u00ecn t\u1eeb chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Arsenal tr\u01b0\u1edbc Chelsea</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4974","checkdouble":"192556"},{"date":"16:05 02/08","title":"3 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c M.U ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh ngay trong tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/1/3-thuong-vu-chuyen-nhuong-co-the-duoc-mu-hoan-thanh-ngay-trong-tuan-nay.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng M.U \u0111ang l\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1 thu h\u00fat s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a NHM Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf tr\u00ean kh\u1eafp th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi trong th\u1eddi gian qua. V\u00e0 li\u1ec7u HLV Mourinho s\u1ebd mang v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t n\u00e0o trong tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y?</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea7y 10 ng\u00e0y n\u1eefa, TTCN c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ea1i Anh s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u00f3ng c\u1eeda. Kh\u00e1c v\u1edbi m\u1ecdi n\u0103m, theo quy \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c L\u0110B\u0110 Anh ban h\u00e0nh, th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/2019 s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00f3ng c\u1eeda v\u00e0o l\u00fac 17h00 ng\u00e0y 9/8 (gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ecba ph\u01b0\u01a1ng), tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u 1 tu\u1ea7n, thay v\u00ec k\u00e9o d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n ch\u00f3t \u0111\u1ebfn ng\u00e0y 31/8 nh\u01b0 trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0 t\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edbm t\u1eadp trung ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 cho CLB. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c TTCN \u0111\u00f3ng c\u1eeda s\u1edbm, \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u0169ng \u0111\u1eb7t ra nh\u1eefng th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf cho nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 Man United trong vi\u1ec7c tr\u00e1nh b\u1ecb c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1c \u00e9p gi\u00e1.</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi M.U l\u00fac n\u00e0y, sau c\u00e1c th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng g\u1ed3m Fred, Diogo Dalot v\u00e0 Lee Grant, HLV Jose Mourinho v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n Old Trafford m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i t\u00ean th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho s\u1ebd thanh l\u00fd g\u1ea5p m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 'ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1eeba' trong th\u1eddi gian n\u00e0y. V\u1eady \u0111\u00e2u s\u1ebd l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng M.U c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh ngay trong tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y?</p>\r\n<h2>3. Matteo Darmian</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"3 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t trong tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"3 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t trong tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/3-thuong-vu-chuyen-nhuong-MU-co-the-hoan-tat-trong-tuan-nay-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng \u1edf c\u1ea3 Anh v\u00e0 Italia \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Matteo Darmian s\u1ebd chia tay M.U ngay trong tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y. M\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia ch\u1ec9 ra s\u00e2n v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 17 tr\u1eadn, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 8 tr\u1eadn t\u1ea1i Premier League.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Mourinho tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng, Matteo Darmian c\u0169ng b\u00e0y t\u1ecf nguy\u1ec7n v\u1ecdng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra \u0111i v\u00e0 Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y. Ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t CLB nh\u01b0 Juventus, Inter v\u00e0 AC Milan \u0111\u1ec1u b\u00e0y t\u1ecf nguy\u1ec7n v\u1ecdng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c mua l\u1ea1i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean l\u00fac n\u00e0y, Inter \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 Sime Vrsaljko, Juve c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Joao Cancelo c\u00f2n AC Milan c\u00f9ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi ng\u00f4i sao M.U. T\u01b0\u1edfng ch\u1eebng Darmian s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i \u1edf l\u1ea1i Old Trafford th\u00eam 6 th\u00e1ng n\u1eefa th\u00ec m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y CLB Napoli \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00eca tay ra v\u1edbi anh. V\u00e0 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 tr\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 b\u00e1o s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra ngay trong tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n<h2>2. Marcos Rojo</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"trung ve Marcos Rojo\" title=\"trung ve Marcos Rojo\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/2/18/everton-duoc-khuyen-tranh-xa-marcos-rojo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a MU \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e1 ch\u1eadt ch\u1ed9i v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 hi\u1ec7n di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Chris Smalling, Phil Jones, Eric Bailly hay Victor Lindelof, Marcos Rojo \u0111ang c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 ph\u1ea3i ra \u0111i trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i gia nh\u1eadp Manchester United t\u1eeb n\u0103m 2014 v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 16 tri\u1ec7u B\u1ea3ng, \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 h\u01a1n 100 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \"Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf\" v\u00e0 t\u1eebng l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch t\u1ea1i UEFA Europa League. Tuy nhi\u00ean, anh v\u1eeba tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y \u00eam \u1ea3 khi ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i ngo\u00e0i v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n 12 l\u1ea7n tr\u00ean t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 Marcos Rojo \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 v\u00e0 g\u00f3p c\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0a Argentina v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng song \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c HLV Mourinho gi\u1eef anh \u1edf l\u1ea1i.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e1c b\u00e1o c\u00e1o g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y cho th\u1ea5y Everton \u0111ang th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina, ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung v\u1ec7 c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i. Theo \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u00e1 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, M.U c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd thu v\u1ec1 kho\u1ea3n ti\u1ec1n 25 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng Anh n\u1ebfu chia tay c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n<h2>1. Toby Alderweireld</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alderweireld\" title=\"Alderweireld\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/12/Chuyen-nhuong-Tottenham-he-2018-Kho-quen-roi,-suong-khong-chiu-duoc!-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede chi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111ang g\u1ea5p r\u00fat chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Toby Alderweireld, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung v\u1ec7 v\u00e0 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i. T\u1eeb l\u00e2u HLV Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 v\u1eefng ch\u1eafc cho \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c Eric Bailly. V\u00e0 Toby Alderweireld l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u01b0a th\u00edch c\u1ee7a anh.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo tin t\u1eeb gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng, l\u00fac n\u00e0y HLV Mourinho \u0111ang \u0111\u1ec3 \u00fd t\u1edbi hai ng\u00f4i sao Maguire v\u00e0 Alderweireld. Tuy nhi\u00ean v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Leicester \u0111ang 'h\u00e9t gi\u00e1' r\u1ea5t cao cho Maguire, Alderweireld \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u1ea1i l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn th\u00edch h\u1ee3p cho Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tottenham \u0111\u00e3 h\u00e9t gi\u00e1 t\u1edbi 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng Anh cho h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00f2n 2 n\u0103m trong h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng n\u00e0y. Tuy nhi\u00ean v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00f3 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 l\u1eabn kinh nghi\u1ec7m nh\u01b0 ng\u00f4i sao tuy\u1ec3n B\u1ec9, \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i con s\u1ed1 qu\u00e1 \u0111\u1eaft.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M.U s\u1ebd d\u00f9ng ti\u1ec1n b\u00e1n Darmian v\u00e0 Rojo \u0111\u1ec3 mua Alderweireld, tuy nhi\u00ean s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o trong s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y ra \u0111i n\u1ebfu th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 M.U chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Tottenham ch\u01b0a ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chuyen-nhuong-mu-hot-nhat-ngay-0208-172-192540.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/2/chuyen-nhuong-mu-hot-nhat-ngay-0208.PNG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chuyen-nhuong-mu-hot-nhat-ngay-0208-172-192540.html\">Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 02/08</span><br>\r\nChuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU 2018 \u0111ang ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u00f4i n\u1ed5i, c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quan t\u00e2m nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 02/08.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tu-bo-maguire-va-alderweireld-mu-muon-mua-mina-cua-barca-172-192523.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/11/tu-bo-maguire-va-alderweireld-mu-muon-mua-mina-cua-barca.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tu-bo-maguire-va-alderweireld-mu-muon-mua-mina-cua-barca-172-192523.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! Bom t\u1ea5n cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a MU \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018</span><br>\r\nMU mua Yerry Mina l\u00e0 mong mu\u1ed1n c\u1ee7a HLV Jose Mourinho, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Colombia nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u201cbom t\u1ea5n\u201d cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/kovacic-khong-den-mu-vi-mourinho-184-192497.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/2/kovacic-khong-den-mu-vi-mourinho.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/kovacic-khong-den-mu-vi-mourinho-184-192497.html\">Sao Real t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i MU v\u00ec Mourinho</span><br>\r\nTheo truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng T\u00e2y Ban Nha, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng Mateo Kovacic quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i gia nh\u1eadp Man United v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng th\u00edch l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i do Mourinho x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4973","checkdouble":"192557"},{"date":"17:24 02/08","title":"B\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch n\u00e0y, M.U s\u1ebd t\u1ed1ng kh\u1ee9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u201cc\u1ee7a n\u1ee3\u201d Martial","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/13/mu-muon-doi-martial-lay-lewandowski-cua-bayern.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M.U mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed5i Martial l\u1ea5y Lewandowski c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0110\u1ee9c mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00f2ng HLV Jose Mourinho song g\u1eb7p tr\u1ee5c tr\u1eb7c \u1edf v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 gi\u00e1 c\u1ea3.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Bayern mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Martial</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBayern Munich \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi Anthony Martial trong v\u00e0i th\u00e1ng qua. H\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1eebng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n Allianz Arena h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Tuy nhi\u00ean, trong khi CLB ch\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n Man United \u0111\u00f2i 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng m\u1edbi nh\u1ea3 Martial th\u00ec Bayern ch\u1ec9 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng tr\u1edf xu\u1ed1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u1ea3n th\u00e2n M.U c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y ch\u00ecm xu\u1ed3ng qu\u00e1 nhanh. H\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n qu\u00e1 m\u1eb7n m\u00e0 trong vi\u1ec7c gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Martial sau nh\u1eefng r\u1eafc r\u1ed1i m\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i g\u00e2y ra. Trong 2 m\u00f9a d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Jose Mourinho, c\u1ef1u th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean Monaco kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0 th\u00f4ng qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"MU mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed5i Martial l\u1ea5y Lewandowski c\u1ee7a Bayern h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"MU mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed5i Martial l\u1ea5y Lewandowski c\u1ee7a Bayern h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/29/MU-muon-doi-Martial-lay-Lewandowski-cua-Bayern-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Martial khi\u1ebfn HLV\u00a0Mourinho r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 v\u1eady v\u1eabn l\u00e0 ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7. Martial v\u1eeba t\u1ea1o ra b\u00ea b\u1ed1i khi kh\u00f4ng quay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp trung \u0111\u00fang h\u1ea1n sau khi r\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00f3n ch\u00e0o s\u1ef1 ra \u0111\u1eddi c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi con th\u1ee9 2. HLV Mourinho r\u1ea5t b\u1ef1c t\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u00f3i v\u00f4 k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o n\u00e0y. Kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng b\u1ecb ph\u1ea1t 2 tu\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u01a1ng, t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ea3u Martial t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Old Trafford c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t m\u1ecbt m\u1edd.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">M.U t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ed5i Martial l\u1ea5y Lewandowski</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Mourinho t\u1eeb l\u00e2u \u0111\u00e3 y\u00eau th\u00edch t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Robert Lewandowski. Nh\u00e2n ti\u1ec7n c\u00f3 Bayern \u0111\u1eb7t v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1, M.U mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed5i Martial l\u1ea5y Lewandowski c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd. Ph\u00eda Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng c\u00e1c th\u00eam m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3n ti\u1ec1n n\u1eefa \u0111\u1ec3 mua l\u1ea1i h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 4 n\u0103m c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Ba Lan.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Niem hy vong so mot cua DT Ba Lan, Robert Lewandowski im tieng trong tran dau nay.\" title=\"Ni\u1ec1m hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a \u0110T Ba Lan, Robert Lewandowski im ti\u1ebfng trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/20/lewandowski-noi-gi-sau-tran-thua-soc-cua-ba-lan-truoc-senegal.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>M.U mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed5i Martial l\u1ea5y Lewandowski</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i Bayern, nh\u1eefng Chelsea v\u00e0 Tottenham c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft t\u1edbi Martial. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, M.U kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u1ea1i ng\u01b0\u1eddi cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f3 tin M.U ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 l\u01b0\u01a1ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c l\u00ean t\u1edbi 500 ngh\u00ecn b\u1ea3ng n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n Lewandowski \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd gia nh\u1eadp. Nh\u01b0ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft, h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn v\u1edbi Bayern tr\u01b0\u1edbc. \u201cH\u00f9m x\u00e1m\u201d c\u00f3 v\u1ebb kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n Lewy, song h\u1ecd c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n Martial thay th\u1ebf l\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1edbng Franck Ribery \u0111\u00e3 35 tu\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng M.U tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-chuyen-nhuong/3-thuong-vu-chuyen-nhuong-co-the-duoc-mu-hoan-thanh-ngay-trong-tuan-nay-187-192557.html\">3 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c M.U ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh ngay trong tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-chuyen-nhuong/mourinho-muon-mu-chieu-mo-bo-doi-cua-real-187-192515.html\">Mourinho mu\u1ed1n M.U chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i c\u1ee7a Real</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/dai-gia-italia-chua-buong-tha-matteo-darmian-172-192507.html\">\u0110\u1ea1i gia Italia ch\u01b0a bu\u00f4ng tha Matteo Darmian</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-bat-ngo-bi-mat-dam-phan-chieu-mo-pogba-180-192489.html\">Barca b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd b\u00ed m\u1eadt \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 sao kh\u1ee7ng MU</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/btc-icc-to-ra-thong-cam-voi-mourinho-ve-luc-luong-172-192359.html\">BTC ICC t\u1ecf ra th\u00f4ng c\u1ea3m v\u1edbi Mourinho v\u1ec1 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4972","checkdouble":"192561"}]}